title: Worlds pick em
body:
I am trying to veiw my world pick em picks but the site is glitching out or something
It keeps switching between the same three pages i just wanna know if i got my pick right

replies.body: You may be having a browser problem causing this, but there are some steps to help clean things up as well as troubleshoot.  As a first step, delete your [cache and cookies](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) to clean up your browser to get you to the right place.  You can also try Incognito mode incase of extension issues, or another browser entirely.  Hope that helps!
